Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:04.51,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,預測預告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:10.14,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,R.O.D THE TV 下一回　「眾紙的黃昏」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:15.91,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,提示“這下慘了”　老師會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:17.61,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,老師知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:21.05,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:24.45,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,慘是很慘沒錯，的確很慘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:25.99,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,李先生到底是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.32,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:28.99,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,李先生到底怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.07,0:00:31.86,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,實在有點慘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:34.43,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,還有眾紙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:39.03,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,不是眾神，而是眾紙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.11,0:00:40.84,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,感到沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:43.71,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,紙也會沮喪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:47.38,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和紙張一起沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:48.71,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,是妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.79,0:00:50.65,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,-姊姊\N-是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:52.65,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，不能用紙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:58.13,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,新的紙張　有時候不小心會割到手對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:00.19,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:01.79,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,割到手指
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.30,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:05.10,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,那的確會很沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.17,0:01:06.10,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:07.50,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是在講這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.50,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,很像耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.57,0:01:10.44,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:11.44,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,-好厲害\N-好聰明喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:12.60,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬，我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.85,0:01:16.94,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣囉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.41,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期，敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.14,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.22,0:01:24.91,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,-那麼，敬請期待囉\N-拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:25.96,preview,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要看喔
